At Pentalog, excellence is what you'll do. We're guided by a mission to positively impact the software development world.
Pentalog is on a quest to find a React.js Developer, the missing piece in our puzzle, for our UK-based client whose forte lies in the AI industry.
Their platform lets customers order the perfect software app for every problem they’re trying to solve. The human-assisted AI platform helps anyone build, run & scale tailor-made software.
