Prior experience in developing desktop applications for Linux, Mac, and Windows platforms;
An advantage would be having knowledge of multiple front-end languages, frameworks, and libraries;
A solid Agile/Scrum mindset, comfortable with rapid iteration and continuous improvement;
A Bachelor's degree in Information Technology or relevant hands-on experience as a Frontend, JavaScript or Fullstack Developer;
Excellent collaboration and teamwork skills;
Outstanding logical thinking and problem-solving abilities;
Good English skills.
